                            target="#t_CEA_1">CEA</gloss>
                    </item>
                    <item>Mr. <persName corresp="#p_MJA_1">John A. McCone</persName>, <gloss
                            target="#t_AEC_1">AEC</gloss>
                    </item>
                    <item>Mr. <persName corresp="#p_AGV_1">George Allen</persName>, <gloss
